com.quest.glue.api.services
Interface WindowsInfoObject

public interface WindowsInfoObject

A single object returned by a WindowsInfoQuery. These objects are copies of the data currently loaded into a result set. They can be safely accessed even after the source result set and connection have been closed. This also means that unlike most other WindowsInfo objects, instances of WindowsInfoObject can be accessed by more than its creating thread.

Note that the names of properties are case sensitive.
